{"tid":1497874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌鳩未撚訓醒既人，心中果團火去撚左邊","createTime":"2019-08-23T07:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T01:05:29.000Z","uid":298052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84c0d31c2105c71cae33820f8f444f55fcf06f80","tid":1497874,"uid":298052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"仲有團火既，發下夢睇下有咩辦法，依家好似停撚停左<br />\n依個星期政府、大企，一係出黎話反暴，一係就出黎護旗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府大企做過d咩撚野，又唔見你跳落海執撚返支旗</span></span>d樓係人住，炒撚到仆街，人工得果雞碎，閪政府有心要幫就唔撚會咁<br />\n大企賺就賺到盡，自已就搵勁撚多，有幾撚多間係良心大企，一隻手都夠數<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有團火既你地，仲縮埋做咩撚野</span></span><br />\n各手足同我記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">黑警可恥 以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba2fdf8a3af8072a77d92c3eb2d203e38e6f78c6","tid":1497874,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"823！"},{"pid":"eb4ff01d828c56d00aef8d5cfb3ee8b2feba3ec7","tid":1497874,"uid":298052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:05:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}